John Redman and Brittany Huber were driving from Georgia to Alabama last spring when he lost control of his car and smashed into a median . 
  Huber was killed on impact and Redman was left clinging to life in a coma . 
  The assistant basketball coach at Dalton State College survived the crash but was told he would be in a wheelchair for the rest of his life . 
  Eleven months later Redman helped lead his team to its first championship title . 
 